# Hatfield runtime/generated directories.
#
# settings.yaml and theme YAML files are tracked so they can be shared
# with the project team. Only transient data is ignored.
#
# If you need custom themes for the whole team, add .yaml files here
# and reference them in settings.yaml, or commit theme YAML files in
# config/themes/ for shared built-in themes.

sessions/
tmp/
rewind/
cache/
logs/
messenger.sqlite
messenger.sqlite-journal
messenger.sqlite-wal
messenger.sqlite-shm
